<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạản̊ta yā rabũ sit̊rī wafīka rāḥatī
 ạảd̊nū maẘlạaya min̊ka ạảjidu taʿ̊zīãtī
 ạản̊tu hūa manāṣī watur̊sīa ạl̊matīn
 fī qas̊waẗi ạlzãmāni ʿin̊dī laka ḥanīn
 ạlqrạr- ạản̊ta tuḥibũnī ạản̊ta tah̊tamũ bī
 wāản̊ta yā rabũ rāʿiⁿ daẘmaⁿạ bī yaʿ̊tanī
 2- ạản̊ta lī gẖun̊watī fī ḍajãẗi ạl̊ḥayāẗ
 ạản̊ta ṣakẖ̊ru najātī ại̹n̊ tẖārati ạl̊mīāh
 ạảf̊takẖiru fī ạlḍĩyqāti ạảf̊raḥu fī kulĩ ḥīn
 fāảnā lạa ạủn̊say̱ min̊ka ạản̊ta ạảbuⁿ ạảmīn
 3- zah̊wu ạl̊ʿum̊ri ạủsalĩmu laka rabī ạlại̹lah
 wāủh̊dī laka qal̊bī ạản̊ta lahu mub̊tagẖāh
 sāảr̊kuḍu lil̊jaʿālaẗi wāủkalĩlu riḥ̊latī
 ḥaẙtẖu mar̊ậka rabĩy yarudũ lī muh̊jatī</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉nt tḥbny</title>
<hymn_number>7708</hymn_number>
<author>bytr wyṣạ, bytr wyṣạ</author>
</song>